{{Infobox scientist |name = Andrius Baltuška |image = |image_size = |caption = Andrius Baltuška |birth_date = {{b-da|26 November 1971}} |birth_place = [[Leningrad]] |residence = |nationality = Lithuanian |death_date = |death_place = |field = [[Laser]] physics |work_institution = [[Technical University of Vienna]] |alma_mater = [[University of Groningen]] |doctoral_advisor = |doctoral_students = |known_for = |prizes = [[Lieben Prize]] |religion = |footnotes = }}'''Andrius Baltuška''' (born 26 November 1971 in [[Leningrad]]) is a [[Lithuania]]n physicist.
